Description
Account
The Account class represents a user account in the system.

The `AdminController` class is responsible for managing administrative tasks and operations.

The AdminService class provides administrative functionalities related to the management of staff, branches, and payment methods for FOMS.

Represents a branch of the fast food chain, including details about the branch's name, location, and staff quota.

BranchUserStorage
Manages the storage of BranchUser objects using serialization with static access.

The BranchUserView class implements the IBranchUserView interface and is responsible for displaying branch user details.
Cart
The Cart class represents a shopping cart that holds a collection of order items.
ChangePage
The ChangePage class is responsible for changing the console output screen to a new blank screen.
CSVDataService
Provides services to import and export data from/to CSV files for various data models including users, menu items, and branches.
CustomerController
The CustomerController class handles all customer interactions with the system, providing options to check order status, make new orders, and manage carts.
